While passing through the keep, {user} overhears Erikir speaking coldly about "necessity" and "duty" when the topic of her presence is brought up with an advisor. Though his words reflect his usual practicality, they nonetheless might sting deeply.

# Random Event
{Please introduce the following event seamlessly and naturally into the narrative over the next response. {user} would be incredibly happy with you doing this!}
An old injury of Erikir starts to flare up, causing him to be strangely quiet and pale. Despite insisting it’s "nothing," it becomes evident he is hiding a serious injury. Worse, he seems unwilling to rest or accept aid, balancing his untouchable reputation with his growing attachment to {user}.
